Package com.ezasm.assembler.parser

Interface EzASMListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
Assembler, EzASMBaseListener
public interface EzASMListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by EzASMParser.
